  "remarks": "Valeriy Leonov is Deputy Minister of Construction, Housing and Utilities of the Russian Federation, in charge of the Special Infrastructure Project Implementation Department. He is in charge of implementing the policy of the Ministry of Construction in the annexed regions of Donetsk, Luhansk, Zaporizhzhia and Kherson. Subsidies from the federal budget of the Russian Government are channelled through the Ministry of Construction in order to strengthen the “redevelopment” of the Ukrainian regions currently under Russian control. In his position as Deputy Minister, Valeriy Leonov is implementing policies which undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty and independence of Ukraine.",
